### Backend — Analytics Service Upgrade

Replace the Phase 1 analytics stub with real aggregate queries.

#### [MODIFY] [analytics.service.ts](file:///home/akai/Desktop/Udemy%20Course%20Finder/backend/src/analytics/analytics.service.ts)
- Replace the stub `getOverview()` with real queries:
  - `totalCourses`: count all courses
  - `totalProviders`: count all providers
  - `activeSources`: count providers where `isEnabled = true`
  - `totalScrapingRuns`: count all log entries
  - `successRate`: `(successful runs / total runs) * 100`
  - `coursesByCategory`: `GROUP BY category.name, COUNT(*)`, ordered by count desc, top 10
  - `coursesByProvider`: `GROUP BY provider.name, COUNT(*)`, ordered by count desc
  - `coursesAddedToday`: count courses with `createdAt >= today midnight`
  - `rejectionReasons`: aggregate from logs (`coursesRejected` totals per provider)
- Return type matches the frontend `AnalyticsOverview` interface

