## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests

```bash
# Backend — ensure all new/modified endpoints work
cd backend && npm run test

# Frontend — lint and type check
cd frontend && npm run lint && npx tsc --noEmit
```

### Manual Verification

1. **Dashboard**: All 5 stat cards show real data. Newest Courses widget shows courses. Expiring Soon widget shows countdown. Auto-refreshes every 30s.
2. **Courses/Browse**: Category and provider filter dropdowns populate correctly. Filters apply and result count updates. Search debounces. Grid/list toggle works. Course cards show category badges and expiry countdowns. Pagination works with filters.
3. **Course Detail**: Page loads with hero, metadata grid, actions. Favorite toggle works with heart animation. "Get Course" opens new tab and records CLICKED history. Share/copy URL works. Related courses display.
4. **Favorites**: Shared CourseCard component renders. Sort options work. Expired filter toggle works. Remove toast shows. "Remove all expired" works.
5. **History**: Action filter tabs work. Date grouping displays correctly. Thumbnails show in table. Clear history with confirmation dialog works.
6. **Sources**: Toast notifications fire on scrape/test/retry/toggle. Timeout is editable and saves. Full log viewer dialog opens with paginated logs. Bulk enable/disable works. Health summary is accurate.
7. **Settings**: Phase 2 reference removed. System info is accurate.
8. **Analytics**: Real data populates all cards. Category and provider breakdowns show actual counts with proportional bars.
9. **Toasts**: Success/error toasts appear for all mutations (favorite, scrape, test, retry, enable/disable).
10. **Responsive**: All pages functional on desktop and tablet viewports.

